          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1627979806129-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low until very gently bubbling and cook, covered, for 15 min</p><p>After 15 min, remove the pot from the heat and keep covered until serving</p><p>Tip: Don't peek! Keep the lid on the whole time to get fluffy and sticky rice!</p><p>Meanwhile, soak the <strong>skewers</strong> in<strong> cold water</strong> (this prevents them from burning whilst cooking)</p>",
